everyday nightclub stuff.

05:27.907 --> 05:29.875
And so, skedaddle.

05:29.943 --> 05:31.310
From what we've heard,

05:31.378 --> 05:34.646
whatever did this was
big, green, and hairy,

05:34.714 --> 05:36.949
but definitely not normal.

05:37.016 --> 05:39.284
I just hope
that thing sticks around

05:39.352 --> 05:42.287
and does some more stomping.
I could use the business.

05:42.355 --> 05:44.189
[Laughs]

05:44.257 --> 05:47.192
