Hey, Crystal Cove!
If you need insurance,

07:04.520 --> 07:08.557
you need to talk to Jax Minner,
your insurance specialist!

07:08.625 --> 07:11.493
So a pair of beast men
attack the town,

07:11.561 --> 07:14.663
and you kids are moping?
What's up, huh?

07:14.731 --> 07:17.232
This kind of stuff usually gets
y'all all hot and bothered.

07:17.300 --> 07:19.034
I'll tell you what's up.

07:19.102 --> 07:20.969
We need to clean up
our emotional

07:21.037 --> 07:23.338
before we can start acting
like a team again.

