Our family always has a pow
wow when we have problems.

07:26.743 --> 07:28.677
- A pow wow?
- For instance,

07:28.745 --> 07:31.346
every time mother starts sleeping
in the back yard tree house,

07:31.414 --> 07:33.682
we hire a doctor or
somebody else with authority

07:33.750 --> 07:35.350
to help us work things out.

07:35.418 --> 07:37.586
Then we lock her away
for a few months.

07:37.654 --> 07:39.688
That's a great idea, Daph.

07:39.756 --> 07:43.025
Omg!

07:43.092 --> 07:45.193
Would you help us, Angel?

07:45.261 --> 07:47.029
Sorry, babies.
Y'all need to get

07:47.096 --> 07:49.431
