08:34.610 --> 08:36.010
Sorry, sheriff.

08:36.078 --> 08:39.014
It was the only way I could think
of to get you to help us out.

08:39.082 --> 08:41.015
Fred, Fred, Fred.

08:41.083 --> 08:43.585
