to make you disappear...

08:48.157 --> 08:50.425
Forever.

08:50.493 --> 08:51.793
I believe you.

08:51.861 --> 08:53.562
Ugh. All right.

08:53.629 --> 08:56.565
Let's get this freak show
over with.

08:56.632 --> 09:00.302
It took 3 clips and a flame
thrower to bring her down.

09:00.370 --> 09:01.903
But let me tell you,

09:01.971 --> 09:04.639
old miss Percy's cat never went
in that tree again.

09:04.707 --> 09:06.308
[Coughs]

09:06.376 --> 09:09.244
