how this is supposed to help us?

09:09.312 --> 09:11.179
Help you?
Oh, yeah.

09:11.247 --> 09:12.614
Uh, let's see.

09:12.682 --> 09:15.450
Uh, my advice is that
you should all leave town

09:15.518 --> 09:17.319
and go your separate ways.

09:17.387 --> 09:18.820
[Grill sizzles]

09:18.888 --> 09:20.822
Not buying it, huh?

09:20.890 --> 09:23.892
Well, what can I say?
I tried.

09:24.894 --> 09:26.361
[Door opens and shuts]

09:26.429 --> 09:29.164
I've had just enough
of this silliness.

09:29.232 --> 09:31.666
We all know the reason
we're having trouble as a group,

09:31.734 --> 09:34.669
and it's spelled
s-h-a-g-g-y.

09:34.737 --> 09:39.107
G... g...
Oh. That's me.

09:39.175 --> 09:41.276
Man up and make up your mind.

09:41.344 --> 09:43.612
Is it going to be me or Scooby?

09:43.679 --> 09:45.947
Yeah, me or Velma?

09:46.015 --> 09:48.617
I'll be ok
with whatever you decide,

09:48.684 --> 09:51.520
