a name.

10:07.837 --> 10:10.439
I suggest we honor those
that came before us.

10:10.506 --> 10:13.942
Mystery, Incorporated.
And to go with our new name,

10:14.010 --> 10:16.845
Team Uniforms!

10:18.114 --> 10:19.514
Oh, boy, Fred.

10:19.582 --> 10:21.550
These are certainly unique.

10:21.617 --> 10:24.219
Thanks, Daph.
I'm pretty proud of them, myself.

10:24.287 --> 10:25.487
Get dressed, everybody.

10:25.555 --> 10:28.123
We've got some humongonauts
to catch.

10:35.598 --> 10:38.033
[Laughter]

10:38.101 --> 10:40.769
[Engine rattles]

10:42.772 --> 10:45.974
We may not know where the
humongonauts are coming from,

10:46.042 --> 10:49.144
but we sure know who's making
money from all their destruction.

10:49.212 --> 10:50.912
That's right, girlie.

10:50.980 --> 10:53.748
I'm making so much money
these days,

10:53.816 --> 10:57.886
I'm thinking of making them
humongo-whatsits partners in my company.

10:57.954 --> 11:00.055
Rimshot!
Ba-doom-kshh!

11:00.123 --> 11:02.090
[Laughs]

11:02.158 --> 11:04.593
If that doesn't make him
sound guilty,

11:04.660 --> 11:06.328
I don't know what does.

11:06.395 --> 11:08.763
It appears we have our suspect.

11:08.831 --> 11:11.500
Uh, I'm still here, you know.

11:11.567 --> 11:13.401
Oh! Sorry.

11:25.114 --> 11:28.049
Ok, gang, remember...
Our goal is to go in,

11:28.117 --> 11:31.219
find proof that Rusty Gnales is
behind the humongonaut attacks,

11:31.287 --> 11:32.954
and then, get out.

11:38.127 --> 11:39.728
