12:31.480 --> 12:34.416
[Grunting]

12:34.483 --> 12:36.418
[Roaring]

12:36.485 --> 12:39.654
What in plantation
is going on out here? Oh!

12:39.722 --> 12:41.756
[Roaring]

12:42.925 --> 12:44.759
[Both grunt]

12:46.429 --> 12:49.598
[Roars]

12:53.102 --> 12:56.104
- [All scream]
- Run!

12:57.206 --> 13:00.475
[All scream]

13:00.543 --> 13:03.979
Phew! Like,
that was a little too close.

13:04.046 --> 13:05.680
[Exhales]
You can say that again.

13:05.748 --> 13:07.182
- That...
- Don't.

13:07.250 --> 13:11.152
I guess this means you're not a
suspect after all, Mr. Gnales.

13:11.220 --> 13:13.722
Gee, you really think so?

13:21.287 --> 13:23.221
That didn't go very well.

13:23.289 --> 13:25.456
And now,
we don't even have a suspect.

13:25.524 --> 13:26.958
Hey, folks, need insurance?

13:27.026 --> 13:28.860
For all of your insurance needs,

13:28.928 --> 13:31.129
be a winner...
contact Max Minner,

13:31.197 --> 13:32.463
the best in the biz.

13:32.531 --> 13:35.133
[Static and stations changing]

13:35.201 --> 13:36.534
Hello!

13:36.602 --> 13:38.203
Mr. E.!

13:38.270 --> 13:39.704
Are you interested in a riddle

13:39.772 --> 13:42.207
that might help you
solve your mystery?

13:42.274 --> 13:44.842
Like, couldn't you just
give us the answer instead?

13:44.910 --> 13:47.345
It'd be a lot easier that way.

13:47.413 --> 13:51.082
[Chuckles] Now, what
would be the fun in that?

13:52.117 --> 13:55.520
To solve the mystery,
do as follows...

13:55.588 --> 13:58.856
Open your eyes
and look for the signs

13:58.924 --> 14:01.192
that are all around you.

14:01.260 --> 14:02.794
Open your ears,

14:02.861 --> 14:04.195
and you'll add

14:04.263 --> 14:05.797
to your knowledge.

14:05.864 --> 14:07.398
Open your minds,

14:07.466 --> 14:09.133
and you'll ensure

14:09.201 --> 14:11.169
a speedy solution.

14:11.237 --> 14:14.806
- Rat's rit?
- Yes, "rat's rit."

14:14.873 --> 14:16.474
Good luck.
[static]

14:16.542 --> 14:19.744
Yes, Max Minner is
your very own insurance pro.

14:19.812 --> 14:20.912
[Clicks]

14:20.980 --> 14:22.747
Does anyone have
the slightest clue

14:22.815 --> 14:24.816
of what Mr. E.
was talking about?

14:27.553 --> 14:29.387
Dad, those humongonaut things...

14:29.455 --> 14:32.223
that... that's
a trademarked name there.

14:33.225 --> 14:34.325
Remember that.

14:34.393 --> 14:37.161
Are super dangerous.
You need to do something.

14:37.229 --> 14:40.231
